Class CodeExecutionWidget

Widget<CodeExecution.WidgetCodeConfig>
public class CodeExecutionWidget
extends AbstractWidget<CodeExecution.WidgetCodeConfig>

Code execution widget for java and groovy code. 1) leveraged nested parameter parsing 2) supports the new groovy classloading 3) uses regular java / groovy reflection (i.e. any method can be called) For a specification and complete usage scenario (e.g. how types can be used), see CodeExecutionWidgetTest. Additional examples can be found in solutions/testBootstrap => test:CodeExecutionWidget Examples: 1. Executing a Java method with signature
